name: Hailwood.nz
tagline: Because apparently I need a website to do things!
body:
### Hey there!
So I was looking to try out sparkpost and got told I need website content before I can send through their service. Go figure.

So now we're here!

![Skydiving Elephants](https://media.giphy.com/media/11CBvrIbpc4IgM/giphy.gif)

### Contact
If you're really looking to get in touch give me a buzz at [matthew@hailwood.nz](mailto:matthew@hailwood.nz) or find me on twitter [@HailwoodNZ](https://twitter.com/hailwoodnz).
